# How to start the Application
To start the application run #python main.py from the root of your folder

# About Application
This is a very simple todo app that works on any terminal
The program allows you to add, update,delete,and view your tasks
Running the main.py file will start the application.

# Where to save your tasks
The program allows you to save your todos to a file specified by you in the terminal
Any update you make to your tasks is updated in the file so far as you are still running the program.

